name: Revelation
description:
A breathtaking beauty of the dawn at the Ayungin Shoal in the controversial West Philippine Sea.

After a long day of voyage, our captain decided to park in this magnificent landscape. All of the crew took their rest while I'm having one of the most solitary moment of my life.

The gradient sky, which mirrors the sea reflects the serenity and tranquility of a soul.

-----------------------

Shot with Mavic 2 Pro
